                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/31/151578876/7ee7a9b2317832622154e3bf7d12ea21_783613230971867959.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "March 31, 2025",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "\"The Fairy of Fondant Felicity? The Towering Tyrant of Taste? Oh, Escoffier's hardly the terror the papers make her out to be. She simply loves cooking, and she can be a bit... strict about it. Is it so surprising that she doesn't respect those who don't take cooking seriously? Don't worry, I just know you'll get along — like cinnamon and vanilla!\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
